%p 
  &bull; <strong>Dr. Peter A. Lewin</strong> joined the delegation of faculty from Drexel's College of Nursing for the annual <a href="https://fninr.memberclicks.net/assets/docs/FNINR%202019%20Gala%20Promo.pdf">Nightingala event</a> on October 23, 2019 in Washington, DC. Close to 1000 attendees representing Nursing Profession nationwide participated. With Dr. Rose Ann DiMaria-Ghalili  (4th from left) as Co-PI, Biomed was awarded a major interdisciplinary NIH grant, which underscores the importance of interdisciplinary research.

